# Excel Model Structure

File: EasyFlow_CFO_P_L_Input.xlsx (also EasyFlow_Financial_Profit_System_2026_ENHANCED.xlsx)
Sheet: Easy_P&L_Input (or INPUT)
Columns B through AW = Jan 2023 through Dec 2026 (48 months).

## Color Coding

- BLUE TEXT = Input cells. Owner enters data here.
- BLACK TEXT = Formulas. Auto-calculated. Do not edit.
- GREEN TEXT = Cross-sheet references.
- NEVER hardcode a calculated value. Always use formulas.

## INPUT Sheet Row Map

| Row | Label | Type |
|---|---|---|
| 5-9 | Revenue lines (Services, Cleaning, Consulting, Workshops, Other) | Input |
| 10 | Interest Income | Input (flag: non-operating, exclude from ratios) |
| 11 | Other Revenue | Input |
| 12 | Total Revenue = SUM(5:11) | Calculated |
| 15-22 | COGS (Subcontractors, Freight, Materials, etc.) | Input |
| 23 | Gross Margin | Calculated |
| 29 | Owner Direct Labor (50% of owner pay) | Input |
| 30-33 | Employee labor lines | Input |
| 34 | Total Direct Labor | Calculated |
| 36 | Direct LPR | Calculated |
| 38 | Contribution Margin | Calculated |
| 42-55 | Marketing lines | Input |
| 56 | Total Marketing | Calculated |
| 62-66 | Facilities (Rent, Utilities, Internet) | Input |
| 70 | Owner Management Wage (50% of owner pay) | Input |
| 76-79 | Payroll taxes and benefits | Input |
| 83-94 | Other OpEx | Input |
| 95 | Total OpEx | Calculated |
| 98 | Pretax Net Income | Calculated |
| 102 | Estimated Tax Rate (config: 0.40) | Config |

## Critical Rules

- Row 102 is a config input (tax rate 0.40), NOT a QBO data target.
- Row 31 is relabeled "Fulfillment Staff 2" (was duplicate of Row 30).
- Row 10 (Interest Income) is recorded but excluded from operating revenue for ratio calculations.
- NEVER write to calculated rows. NEVER write to section header rows.
- When importing monthly data, aggregate weekly/daily to monthly first.
- Owner pay split: Row 29 + Row 70 must equal total owner pay exactly. Use floor + subtraction.
